%X We designed, implemented, and evaluated a new concept for visualizing and
searching databases utilizing direct manipulation called dynamic queries. 
Dynamic queries allow users to formulate queries by adjusting graphical
widgets, such as sliders, and see the results immediately.  By providing a
graphical visualization of the database and search results, users can find
